### Current Behavior

Our company installs NoMachine on our dev systems which (or a dependecy of it) adds the environment variable  `NX_RUNNER `with the value `/usr/NX/bin/nxrunner` . And this is now conflicting with the nrwl/nx  `NX_RUNNER`. 

As a  workaround I could just set the param `-runner default`, but maybe somebody has a better idea?

### Expected Behavior

Don't know

